# Register (or update) a handoff site in the server's registry. The
# record is consumed at goal time by HandoffTransfer, HotelTransfer,
# and MoveResource(to_handoff). Set ``replace_existing=true`` to
# overwrite a name that already exists; otherwise a collision is
# rejected with success=false.
Handoff handoff
bool replace_existing
---
bool success
string message
